body
.content
  .push.mt-5
  .container.p-5.page.rounded-lg
    .row.no-gutters
      .col-12
        h3 Messageboard
      
      //- .form-group.row
      //-   label.col-2.col-form-label(for='example-datetime-local-input') From date
      //-   .col-10
      //-     input#example-datetime-local-input.form-control(type='datetime-local', value='2011-08-19T13:45:00')
      .col-12
        
        form.form-inline.float-right.row
          .col-6
            label.sm(for='inlineFormInput') From date:
            input#inlineFormInput.form-control.mb-2.mr-sm-2.ml-sm-2.form-control-sm(type='text' disabled="")
          .col-6
            label.sm(for='inlineFormInputGroup') To date:
            input#inlineFormInputGroup.form-control.mr-sm-2.ml-sm-2.mb-2.form-control-sm(type='text' disabled="")
          
        
      
      .row.ml-0.mr-0.mt-0.mb-4.shadow.bg-white.rounded-lg.p-0.col-12
        // Table
        table(role='table')#tablePreview.table.table-striped.table-hover.mb-0
          // Table head
          thead(role='rowgroup')
            tr(role='row')

              th(role='columnheader').w-20 Mark as read
              th(role='columnheader').w-20 Name
              th(role='columnheader').w-40 Subject
              th(role='columnheader').w-10 Date
              th(role='columnheader').w-10 Time
          // Table head
          // Table body
          tbody.message(role='rowgroup')
            tr.accordion-toggle(data-toggle='collapse',aria-expanded="true", data-target='#demo1',onclick='messageOne()')
              td.custom-control.custom-checkbox.mx-0.text-center
                input#customCheck1.custom-control-input.position-relative(type='checkbox')
                label.custom-control-label(for='customCheck1')
              td Admin
              td Message#1
              td#inbox1
              td#time1
            tr
              td.hiddenRow.p-0(colspan='6')
                #demo1.accordian-body.collapse.p-4  Mr. Huang has complained people have stolen his property, but he has dementia and we canâ€™t find any evidence this has actually happened. Please make sure you always enter his room with two people so there is a witness to all activity.
            tr.accordion-toggle(data-toggle='collapse',aria-expanded="true", data-target='#demo2',onclick='messageTwo()')

              td.custom-control.custom-checkbox.mx-0.text-center
                input#customCheck2.custom-control-input.position-relative(type='checkbox')
                label.custom-control-label(for='customCheck2')
              td Admin
              td Message#2
              td#inbox2
              td#time2
            tr 
              td.hiddenRow.p-0(colspan='6')
                #demo2.accordian-body.collapse.p-4  Dear valued staff member,
                  |
                  br
                  |There is a compulsory meeting today in the staff room at 14:00.
                  | All staff are required to attend.



      .row.p-0.m-0.float-right
        a.btn.btn-primary.float-right(onclick='route()')  Proceed
        //a.btn.btn-primary(href='foodrecord.html')  Add New


#messageModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1' role='dialog' aria-labelledby='MessageBoardErrorModal' aria-hidden='true')
  .modal-dialog(role='document')
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        h5#messageModalLabel.modal-title Notice
        button.close(type='button' data-dismiss='modal' aria-label='Close')
          span(aria-hidden='true') &times;
      .modal-body
        | Please read all messages to proceed
      .modal-footer
        button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button' data-dismiss='modal') Close
